10/stevie-nicks-fleetwood-mac-barbie-2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/stevie-nicks-fleetwood-mac-barbie-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/stevie-nicks-fleetwood-mac-barbie-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/stevie-nicks-fleetwood-mac-barbie-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">史蒂夫·尼克斯 (Stevie Nicks)</a>宣布美泰 (Mattel) 根据<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fleetwood-mac">弗利特伍德麦克 (Fleetwood Mac)</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/20-things-you-might-not-know-about-fleetwood-macs-rumours-761363">谣言</a>》封面艺术中的造型制作了官方芭比娃娃。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/20-things-you-might-not-know-about-fleetwood-macs-rumours-761363">关于 Fleetwood Mac 的“谣言”你可能不知道的 20 件事</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位独奏者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stevie-nicks-announces-2023-headline-tour-dates-3385516#:~:text=Stevie%20Nicks%20has%20unveiled%20a,headlining%20jaunt%20with%20Billy%20Joel.&amp;text=Nicks'%20joint%20tour%20with%20Joel,shows%20between%20March%20and%20September.">将于今年 12 月结束当前的巡演</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stevie-nicks-announces-2024-north-american-headlining-tour-3503894">明年再次踏上北美之路</a>，她昨晚（10 月 1 日）在纽约市麦迪逊广场花园的演出中告诉观众，当芭比玩具制造商出现时，她“不知所措”美泰（通过<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/stevie-nicks-announces-new-barbie-madison-square-garden-1234836494/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>）向她提出了这个想法。</p><p>在表演完《贝拉·唐娜》后，尼克斯说道：“我有一些非常令人兴奋的事情要在世界其他地方之前几个小时与大家分享。”</p><p>她在演讲中表示，美泰一年前找到了她。 “我非常不知所措，”尼克斯说。 “她会像我一样吗？她会拥有我的灵魂吗？她会得到我的心吗？”</p><p>然后她与粉丝分享说，在过去的三个月里，她一直带着一个用她的肖像制成的芭比娃娃在路上。</p><p> “当我看着她时，我看到了 27 岁时的自己，”这位歌手说道，并补充说，她也看到了自 1975 年以来自己所经历的一切。“我就是她，她就是我。”</p><p>尼克斯向粉丝们展示了这个娃娃，并将其赠送给观众中一位名叫萨拉的人，这也促使她唱了几句弗利特伍德麦克公司的同名歌曲。</p><p>美泰今天（10 月 2 日）正式推出了芭比娃娃，作为其招牌音乐系列的一部分。该娃娃零售价为 55 美元。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cx4drJ3r_fh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.057 562.106,71.106 